Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.02,0:00:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.52,0:00:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said before that there'd be no secrets between us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.57,0:00:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.44,0:00:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never lie to you ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't lie to me either, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.87,0:00:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what happened between you and Yamamoto-san in middle school?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.01,0:00:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the same reason you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's making me uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.10,0:00:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't going to be any secrets between us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.18,0:00:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.77,0:00:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.19,0:00:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you answer me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.64,0:02:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like some more tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.77,0:02:58.74,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, knock before coming in...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.01,0:01:23.89,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Usotsuki na anata nakimushi no atashi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:29.86,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doushite umaku ikanai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.86,0:01:35.99,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshare shita kami mo rain suton no tsume mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:41.95,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata wa kidzuki mo shinai ne
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:49.33,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love kanashii namida nanka ja nai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.33,0:01:54.05,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Me ga kawaite hirihiri suru dake
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.05,0:01:59.97,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono unmei bakari I love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:08.85,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi dake wo atashi dake wo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:13.77,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Atsui omoi wo uketomete
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:20.91,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doko made mo tsunagattetai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:27.66,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawaikunai nakigao mo se mo aishiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.01,0:01:23.89,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't things go well between
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:29.86,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,the liar, you, and the crybaby, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.86,0:01:35.99,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't notice my styled hair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:41.95,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,or my nice set of press-on nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:49.33,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love isn't about the unhappy tears that go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.33,0:01:54.05,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tears only leave my eyes dry and hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.05,0:01:59.97,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:08.85,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,between only you and only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:13.77,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to accept your hot feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:20.91,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,and be taken by you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:27.66,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite your uncute, tearful face and your shortness, I still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:03:02.24,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,800)\pos(140,384)}Episode 8 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:02.24,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,I completely forgot that I had received this cake recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, we're full... give us a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, but I went through all the trouble to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but could I use your bathroom for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! It's down the stairs to your right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about bad timing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm really sorry about this... My mom just doesn't know when to back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we finish where we left off?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Ah... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.55,0:04:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were we again? Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I answer, I'd first like to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think happened between us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you suddenly ask me like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ask me that, I don't know... that's why I asked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto and I were in the same class all three years of middle school, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my seat was next to hers once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since our student numbers were close, we were the daily helpers together every once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We hardly ever spoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We never had any fights, and neither of us confessed love to each other or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The scale of your question's too wide that I can't answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any other questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Yamamoto-san... love you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first time I've ever heard anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During the field trip...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you touched Yamamoto-san's forehead without a single drop of hesitation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's been bugging me this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might've been jealous of her the entire time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano... how do you feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what I wanted to ask the most this whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...about Yamamoto-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.74,0:05:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care whether Yamamoto loved or hated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with me. Not interested one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the opposite of "love" isn't hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was nothing between you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course there wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...wanted him to reassure me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that everything would be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano I... believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:07:01.69,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1900,0)\fscx180\fscy175\c&HF1F1F2&\frx26\fry16\pos(312,160)\frz359.524}City Bus
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you later tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Takahashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:08:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked Yano directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just like you said, Takeuchi-kun. He said there was nothing between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi, you worry too much about those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a lot, Takeuchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, there's no way you wouldn't have noticed something happening, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You changed your bangs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, I tried splitting them. Does it look strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:44.12,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HB3A1CB&\fscx151.25\fscy138.75\frz8.927\frx14\fry346\pos(373,202)}Girl's Bathroom
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said I look cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana, did you finally do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano came to your place, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:09:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't done anything yet... That's still a long way off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano's being forced to hold back, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is it all that strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... "to each her own" is my motto. So I guess it's all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, but... the pressure's building up more and more every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you against it, Nana?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not exactly against it, I'm just not really sure how I feel about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike Yano, it's not like it's always welling up inside me all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So when he suggests doing it, it's a little scary, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it doesn't well up in you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I totally agree with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana, you don't have to push yourself to do it. Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to hurry up and get a boyfriend, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, that's what Mizu-chin said, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moving onto question #5... Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're up for question #5, part A.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Question #5, question #5...
