Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the translation?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was so beautiful that... umm... I wanted to make friends with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Now replace that underline phrase with another expression that has the same meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was so beautiful that I wanted to... to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make... friends with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Intimacy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go out with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Get acquainted with..."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Get acquainted with."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? Didn't you do the assignment?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to... to... make love with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:55.67,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\c&H3D403E&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fscx203.75\fscy212.5\pos(319,372)}"I wanted to make love with her."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:11:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... grammatically, it isn't wrong, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you come up with another phrasing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:03.89,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\c&H3D403E&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fscx203.75\fscy212.5\pos(324,380)}"Fuck her."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it all really has built up inside him...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... he's really holding it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Nana's gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she'll reach her limit sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, there is that story about Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah, you're talking about that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.47,0:11:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does Nana know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we should keep it a secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...from Nana.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:47.35,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&H40&\c&HFFFFFF&\fscx156.25\fscy141.25\pos(413,287)\frz343.272\frx352\fry346}Dispenser
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A story about him...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lend me your Math textbook?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? At least knock first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't even ring the doorbell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me for intruding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be on the shelf over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unusual for you to ask, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl sitting next to me wouldn't show me hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, maybe in one of the drawers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get a haircut?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just changed the mousse I use.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Organize your stuff, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's sitting next to you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with both you and Takahashi asking about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's suspicious of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She thinks something happened between Yamamoto and me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when nothing like that did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna borrow this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:13:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you two go home together that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding hands, you went over to her house, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.74,0:13:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We went to put some up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for failing to meet your expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Motoharu! Don't you think you can fool me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...did you pretend not to know until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't pretend not to know. You simply didn't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...could you do it with her little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... her room, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm using it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun comes in best through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan's room is now over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it's now the family altar room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana, I hear you're finally going over to Yano's today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just going to do a report together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But his parents won't be around!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they weren't, I wouldn't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:15:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! You're his girlfriend, so have so more confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana-chan, wanna get some steamed meat buns at the convenience store?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not hungry, so don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to be in a bad mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana-chan. Is looking at the scenery fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's the swimming school I used to go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? When was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Till my first year of middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Why?", because there was a really fast guy I could never beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought it was stupid, and quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... so unless you're first, you're never satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So hey... what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? It's a hand. Mine, to be more specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it look like a foot to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, quit the lame jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:15:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They look so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like they don't have a care in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we seem to keep...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...running into one problem after another?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me for intruding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:45.40,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\frz24.145\frx8\fry358\c&H666E72&\move(225,388,225,355,0,7739)}Motoharu.\NI'm going to my doctor's appointment.\NI'm going shopping after that, so I might\Nbe a little late. Your dinner is ready and\Nwaiting in the freezer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:40.27,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,"Motoharu, I'm going to my doctor's appointment."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:43.06,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm going shopping after that, so I might be a little late."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:45.40,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,"Your dinner is ready and waiting in the freezer."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's out for the day...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You tricked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! This is pure coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, it's not what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying! You're trying to get back at me for the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a moron? If I was gonna do that, I would've done it fair and square!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "If I was gonna do that"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:05.25,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,God... will I be able to protect myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in this house today?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me repeat myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So could you sit... a little closer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... it's hot in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you take off your sweater?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:26.77,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fscx263.75\fscy223.75\pos(547,351)\c&H46596A&\b1}Wasn't\Nreally\Nimplying\Nanything\N...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black tea's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One spoon of sugar, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you trap the steam, it tastes better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a clean kitchen...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:18:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels kinda strange when two of us stand here like this, like we're married or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.48,0:18:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of stupid things am I thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having a delusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she feeling better?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom and dad started going out in high school, and got married after ten years of dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You serious? That's hard to believe. I'm surprised it lasted so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess me and Yano getting married after going out together...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...might only be the unrealistic delusion I thought it was, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... the person standing here ten years from now may not be me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit next to me, Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more my love for him increases, the more lonely I think I'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay. I won't say anything to make you uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:20.22,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fscx112.5\fscy111.25\frz228.171\frx36\fry340\move(289,66,343,65,0,7991)}English
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't screw around when we're working on English.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hide my gum in a place where you can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I won't touch you at all today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.93,0:19:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't... Can you really just change your principles for one girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't for my friends and other people, but for a woman, I can change them as much as necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are my principles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, why don't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.37,0:19:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...tell me why you're in such a bad mood today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During middle school...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is it true that you had sex with Nana-san in school gym?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's not one thing, it's another...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I was saying, you did, didn't you? In the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...intend to blame you for things in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since there's nothing I can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm jealous of Yano's past, there's nothing I can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even ten years from now, Yano will still be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should already know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why do I still feel I want Yano all for myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.03,0:21:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...didn't bug me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close, that was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I almost touched you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:19.50,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fscx106.25\fscy115\frz346.638\pos(379,91)\c&H495A6A&\frx38\fry0}Math I
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:19.63,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fscx106.25\fscy115\frz346.638\pos(379,91)\c&H495A6A&\frx38\fry0\clip(m 360 64 l 354 95 384 99 397 70)}Math I
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be hard for me to hold back if I sit close to you, so I'll sit on the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to keep my promise, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could rewrite my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could, I'd do all I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if it would stop you from crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.91,0:21:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My past won't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.99,0:21:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... we need to make my past pale in comparison to our present.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.80,0:22:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted... to make someone my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.43,0:22:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I say some pretty stuff now now and then, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.98,0:22:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.10,0:22:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's fine by me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.24,0:22:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.03,0:22:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.62,0:22:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you mean sex?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.33,0:22:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.32,0:23:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'm caught in the flow of it all...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.37,0:23:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.63,0:23:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see any reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.30,0:23:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to hold these feelings back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.76,0:22:54.72,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Taisetsu na anata no hitomi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.72,0:23:01.77,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Watashi wa utsutteru no ka na
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.48,0:23:13.20,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimorehi zashikomu madobe ni wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:20.50,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doushite yasashiku narerun darou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.79,0:23:27.63,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kokoro kakushite kodou kakushite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:29.93,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsumo no you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:36.31,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Wakariaenai tsurasa ga tamaranai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.31,0:23:45.52,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Waraitai waraitai kokoro no mannaka de
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.52,0:23:50.03,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata ni wa uchiakeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.03,0:23:54.62,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuyogaru watashi yowaki na watashi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.62,0:24:00.21,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinou no hanashi dou demo ii koto mo zenbu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.21,0:24:05.04,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Aishiteru kore kara mo zuttoo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.04,0:24:11.38,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Ude wo kunde aruite ikou YEAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.48,0:24:25.36,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi wo sagashite kimi wo sagashite
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.36,0:24:31.61,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna toki demo kimi wo sagashiteiru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.61,0:24:36.78,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsukaru no sore wa kimi na no?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.78,0:24:47.75,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanashikute kanashikute nakidashisou ni naru
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.75,0:24:56.26,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Dore dake no omoi nara dakishimete kureru no?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.26,0:25:01.68,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah waraitai waraitai
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.68,0:25:06.23,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Nani mo ka mo nagesutete
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.23,0:25:10.94,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata ni wa uchiakeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.94,0:25:15.07,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinou no hanashi ashita no hanashi
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.07,0:25:20.95,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Futari no mirai kakaekirenai hodo zenbu
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.95,0:25:25.46,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Yakusoku wa shinakutemo ii yo
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.46,0:25:32.26,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Futari massugu ni arukou YEAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.76,0:22:54.72,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'm reflected
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.72,0:23:01.77,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,in your precious eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.48,0:23:13.20,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how I can always be happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:20.50,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,on the windowsill where the sunshine always falls?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.79,0:23:27.63,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I hide my true feelings and the thumping of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:29.93,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,As always,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:36.31,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,the pain of being able to understand each other burns.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.31,0:23:45.52,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to smile, I want to smile, down to the core of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.52,0:23:50.03,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll open up to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.03,0:23:54.62,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,about how I pretend to be strong, about how I'm weak,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.62,0:24:00.21,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,about what happened yesterday, about everything that means nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.21,0:24:05.04,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll continue to love you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.04,0:24:11.38,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Take my arm and let's walk. Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.48,0:24:25.36,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I look for you, I look for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.36,0:24:31.61,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always looking for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.61,0:24:36.78,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,but when I find that person, is it really you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.78,0:24:47.75,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sad, I'm so sad, I could cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.75,0:24:56.26,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,How much feeling must I give to be able to embrace you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.26,0:25:01.68,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I want to smile, I want to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.68,0:25:06.23,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Throwing everything away,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.23,0:25:10.94,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll open up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.94,0:25:15.07,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,About yesterday, about tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.07,0:25:20.95,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,about our future and everything, so much that I can't even take it all myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.95,0:25:25.46,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to promise me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.46,0:25:32.26,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just keep walking. Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.96,0:25:34.98,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HDC6CE3&\c&HFDE2FF&\fscx97.5\fscy122.5\pos(450,377)}Episode 9 Preview...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.40,0:25:09.73,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, it's come to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.94,0:25:13.49,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't know\N how it's come to this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.49,0:25:21.04,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,...I really don't understand\N how I was the one to suggest it...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.37,0:25:25.46,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, geez!\N He's already getting naked!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.46,0:25:27.92,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're scared, we can stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.96,0:25:32.21,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Please make me your own.
